WEBVTT

00:05:30.056 --> 00:05:31.487
You ready for the next flag?

00:05:33.590 --> 00:05:34.769
Right.

00:05:34.793 --> 00:05:36.196
Take a moment.

00:05:36.220 --> 00:05:39.433
Really examine how you felt
when this hit the screen.

00:05:40.488 --> 00:05:42.569
I'm going to change
the slide pretty quickly

00:05:42.593 --> 00:05:45.151
so you don't take pictures of me
in front of this one.

00:05:45.175 --> 00:05:46.176
(Laughter)

00:05:46.200 --> 00:05:47.351
Alright?

00:05:47.375 --> 00:05:50.293
So Germany after World War I,

00:05:50.317 --> 00:05:52.323
it was in a pretty bad state,

00:05:52.347 --> 00:05:57.171
and a young Adolf Hitler had a lot of --
let's call them -- "ideas,"

00:05:57.195 --> 00:06:00.006
of how Germany got to where they'd gotten